SIC codes in the ranges 54110000-54110199, 54110300-54119999 AND [employees<5 AND sales<$2million or sales=missing]. Employees must be non-missing. If employees<5, then sales could be missing. For sales and employees, the most recent value for these was used if these changed over time.
If BKN = 1 or BKS = 1 then BKA = 1

Meets one of the following criteria:
1) SIC codes 54000000-54999999, 55400000-55499999, 58000000-58999999, 59630100-59630299, 65120200-65120299 AND Trade Name on the Technomics/R&I list for segment of “Quick Service” and Menu as “Doughnuts,” “Specialty,” or “Frozen Desserts.”
2) SIC codes 54000000-54999999, 58000000-58999999 AND Company on the Technomics/R&I list for segment of “Quick Service” and Menu as “Doughnuts,” “Specialty,” or “Frozen Desserts.”
Chain name list can be found in the appendix (31 chain names).
If CFN = 1 or CFS = 1 then CFA = 1

Meets one of the following criteria:
1) SIC codes 54000000-54999999, 55400000-55499999, 58000000-58999999, 59630100-59630299, 65120200-65120299 AND Trade Name on the Technomics/R&I list for either segment of “Quick Service” or “Fast Casual” and Menu is “Coffee,” “Coffee Café,” or “Coffee/Tea.”
2) SIC codes 54000000-54999999, 58000000-58999999 AND Company on the Technomics/R&I list for either segment of “Quick Service” or “Fast Casual” and Menu is “Coffee,” “Coffee Café,” or “Coffee/Tea.”

Meets one of the following criteria:

SIC codes in the ranges 54110000-54110199, 54110300-54119999 AND {[employees>=5 AND employees<25] or employees=missing]] and [sales<$2million or sales=missing]}. If employees is missing and sales is not missing, then sales must be <$2million. If sales is missing and employees is not missing, then employees is between 5-24. If both employees and sales is missing, then that record will be coded as ‘GRY’ here. For sales and employees, the most recent value for these was used if these changed over time.
